    <title>jolin</title>
    <link href="https://ametoyuki098.github.io/nlozop/jolin/"/>
    <id>https://ametoyuki098.github.io/nlozop/jolin/</id>
    <published>2025-10-24T02:58:43.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-11-26T04:12:34.386Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>介绍：此博文记录在安卓手机（平板）termux中安装配置hexo博客的过程，主题使用以及托管。</p><h2 id="准备工作："><a href="#准备工作：" class="headerlink" title="准备工作："></a>准备工作：</h2><p>开始之前，请确保已准备好以下内容：</p><ul><li>Termux （<a href="https://f-droid.org/packages/com.termux">F-Droid</a>或<a href="https://github.com/termux/termux-app">GitHub</a>仓库中安装）</li><li>域名 （可选）</li><li>GitHub账号</li><li>Cloudflare （可选）</li></ul><h2 id="安装必要环境"><a href="#安装必要环境" class="headerlink" title="安装必要环境"></a>安装必要环境</h2><p><strong>启动Termux应用后，请按顺序输入以下命令，以完成初始设置并安装所需的运行环境：</strong></p><div class="note info modern"><p>termux本身会触发系统弹窗，要求用户授权存储访问权限。如果没有需要执行<code>termux-setup-storage</code>指令后授权。另外还需要手动开启通知权限</p></div><ol><li><p>更换软件源以免出现网络问题</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">termux-change-repo</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">先选 Single mirror → Tsinghua 空格是选择回车是确认</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>更新Termux的包信息和版本</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg update &amp;&amp; pkg upgrade</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>若过程中出现提示，通常直接按回车（默认）即可</p></li><li><p>安装<strong>nodejs</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg install nodejs-lts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="hexo安装与初始化"><a href="#hexo安装与初始化" class="headerlink" title="hexo安装与初始化"></a>hexo安装与初始化</h2><p><strong>依次执行官方的安装操作</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class="line">hexo init blog</span><br><span class="line">cd blog</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><u> <code>blog</code>只是一个示例，你可以改成如<code>demobolg</code> <code>myblog</code>…等其它自定义名称</u></p><h3 id="生成启动本地预览"><a href="#生成启动本地预览" class="headerlink" title="生成启动本地预览"></a>生成启动本地预览</h3><p><code>hexo clean</code>清理静态文件<br><code>hexo generate</code>生成静态文件<br><code>hexo server</code>开启本地预览<br>也可以简写成：<code>hexo cle,hexo g,hexo s</code></p><p>执行完成后会返回一个预览地址<br><u><em><a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/</a></em></u>复制在浏览器打开，就能看见博客。</p><p><strong>图片</strong></p><div class="note warning modern"><p>注意：若无法查看；在通知中获取唤醒锁或执行<code>termux-wake-lock</code> 另外可能需设置<strong>允许高耗电</strong>，<strong>忽略电池优化</strong></p></div><h3 id="文件夹结构"><a href="#文件夹结构" class="headerlink" title="文件夹结构"></a>文件夹结构</h3><div class="note modern"><p>当你在博客根目录使用ls列出文件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> .</span><br><span class="line">├── _config.landscape.yml</span><br><span class="line">├── _config.yml</span><br><span class="line">├── db.json</span><br><span class="line">├── node_modules</span><br><span class="line">├── package-lock.json</span><br><span class="line">├── package.json</span><br><span class="line">├── scaffolds</span><br><span class="line">├── source</span><br><span class="line">├── themes</span><br><span class="line">└── yarn.lock</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>当你在博客根目录使用ls列出文件</em></p><ul><li>其中<code>_config.yml</code>是hexo主配置内容，管理全局设置，部署等…</li><li><code>source</code>是存放创建的文章和页面。</li><li>然后是<code>public</code>，当用户执行<code>hexo g</code>后所生成的静态文件就存放在该目录下，编辑_config.yml可以自定义生成目录。</li><li>其余文件和目录是一些依赖和管理。</li></ul></div><p>通过以上步骤，博客基础就算搭建完成。但目前还是只能在本地开发预览，接下来是通过静态托管实现全网访问。</p><h2 id="静态托管"><a href="#静态托管" class="headerlink" title="静态托管"></a>静态托管</h2><p><u><a href="https://github.com/">https://github.com</a></u>前往该地址，使用邮箱注册一个Github账户。</p><h3 id="Git"><a href="#Git" class="headerlink" title="Git"></a>Git</h3><p>安装Git</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg install git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再执行两行命令配置Git用户信息（替换自己的邮箱和用户名）</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config user.name &quot;Github用户名&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config user.email &quot;Github绑定邮箱&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="新建仓库"><a href="#新建仓库" class="headerlink" title="新建仓库"></a>新建仓库</h3><p>这里需要一个超链接）<br>在GitHub主页点击<code>New</code>创建一个新仓库<br>仓库名填写你创建时填写的<code>用户名+github.io</code>其他保持默认。<br><strong>图片</strong><br>完成后你会看到有<code>SSH,HTTPS</code>两种地址，后面我们会使用到其中之一用于推送操作</p><p>用编辑器打开<code>_config.yml</code>文件</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nano _config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在开头部分找到<code>url</code>改成:</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="string">https://用户名/github.io</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再找到<code>deploy</code>配置项，将其中的<code>repo</code>字段替换为你自己的仓库地址。完成后<code>Ctrl + X + Y</code>然后回车退出。</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:ametoyuki098/ametoyuki098.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">main</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装部署插件<code>npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</code></p><p>接下来是申请密钥并添加公钥到GitHub。如果你使用的不是ssh，则需要去GitHub申请一个身份令牌供推送使用。下面是两种方式的操作</p><h3 id="验证"><a href="#验证" class="headerlink" title="验证"></a>验证</h3><div class="tabs"><div class="nav-tabs"><button type="button" class="tab active"><i class="fa-solid fa-key"></i>SSH</button><button type="button" class="tab"><i class="fa-solid fa-address-card"></i>TOKEN</button></div><div class="tab-contents"><div class="tab-item-content active"><p>安装OpenSSH:</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg install openssh -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>生成密钥对</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C &quot;GitHub绑定邮箱&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里执行后会询问保存路径和密码保护，直接回车默认即可。</p><p><code>cat ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub</code>执行此命令输出公钥至终端（复制输出的全部内容）</p><p><strong>图片</strong></p><div class="note default modern"><p>GitHub网页右上角头像 → Settings（设置） → （左侧找到）SSH and GPG keys</p></div>点击 `New SSH key` 取一个标题，然后将刚刚复制的公钥粘贴并保存<p><strong>图片</strong></p><p><code>ssh -T git@github.com</code>该命令测试连接<br>首次执行会弹出提示，输入 yes 回车即可；若<br>输出：<code>Hi ametoyuki098! You&#39;ve successfully authenticated...</code>说明配置成功</p><p><strong>图片</strong></p></div><div class="tab-item-content"><h3 id="https"><a href="#https" class="headerlink" title="https"></a>https</h3><div class="note default modern"><p>GitHub右上角头像 → Settings → 左侧底部Developer settings → Personal access tokens → 选Token classic → 点击Generate new token（选择classic）</p></div>**图片**最后上滑屏幕点击`Generate token`按照以上步骤找到并申请身份令牌，**令牌创建成功只会显示一次，务必保存好**<p>此时在进行<code>hexo d</code>推送操作，在输入用户名后提示输入密码便是此令牌，粘贴回车便可推送。</p><p>可以把令牌放入配置中，以免每一次推送都需要手动输入；编辑器打开<code>nano _config.yml</code></p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">https://&lt;TOKEN&gt;@github.com/&lt;USERNAME&gt;/&lt;REPO&gt;.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">main</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>找到deploy配置项，在repo字段把<code>&lt;TOKEN&gt;</code>替换为你刚刚生成的令牌，<code>&lt;USERNAME&gt;</code> <code>&lt;RERO&gt;</code>替换成你的用户名和仓库名。</p><p>但是这种方式令牌是明文写在<code>_config.yml</code>中。推荐使用环境变量的方式写入：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">https://$GITHUB_TOKEN@github.com/&lt;USERNAME&gt;/&lt;RERO&gt;.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">main</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>&lt;USERNAME&gt; &lt;RERO&gt;</code>修改成你自己的用户名和仓库名。</p><p>终端执行这个命令设置环境变量</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">echo &#x27;export GITHUB_TOKEN=你的token&#x27; &gt;&gt; ~/.bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></div><div class="tab-to-top"><button type="button" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div></div><div class="note success modern"><p>如成功推送，届时你可以访问<a href="https://username.github.io(username更换为你自己的用户名)/">https://username.github.io（username更换为你自己的用户名）</a></p></div><h2 id="主题"><a href="#主题" class="headerlink" title="主题"></a>主题</h2><blockquote><p><a href="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/21cfbf15/"><code>Butterfly</code></a>主题为此次演示。更多的主题样式你可以查看<a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">Hexo主题预览</a></p></blockquote><p>你可以使用npm或Git的方式安装主题，这里大概过一下。<br>而更详细以及主题后续配置请前往：<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/">https://butterfly.js.org</a></p><p>使用npm</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-theme-butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用Git</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone -b master https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly.git themes/butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>为了后续流程建议使用npm安装主题</p><hr><p>安装渲染插件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="设置主题"><a href="#设置主题" class="headerlink" title="设置主题"></a>设置主题</h3><ol><li><p>编辑博客主目录下<code>_config.yml</code>文件，找到<code>theme</code>字段并修改为：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">butterfly</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>执行以下命令，就能在本地看见主题效果</p></li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h3><p>为了后续配置方便，需要把主题的配置文件复制到博客根目录并改名为<code>_config.butterfly.yml</code>。 根据安装方式执行对应命令（请确保你处在博客根目录）</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cp node_modules/hexo-theme-butterfly/_config.yml ./_config.butterfly.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cp themes/butterfly/_config.yml ./_config.butterfly.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>你可以尝试用编辑器打开<code>_config.butterfly.yml</code>这个文件，并找到<code>index_img</code>字段修改为：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">index_img: https://87c80b6.webp.li/i/2025/04/11/13d</span><br><span class="line">xcy-x7.jpg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当再执行<code>hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</code>主页被设置成一张图片</p><p>这就是butterfly主题的基本安装。而配置说明，需要你自行阅读<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/4aa8abbe/">butterfly主题配置</a>这篇文章。</p><h2 id="自动部署：GitHub-Actions"><a href="#自动部署：GitHub-Actions" class="headerlink" title="自动部署：GitHub Actions"></a>自动部署：GitHub Actions</h2><div class="note success flat"><p>在本节步骤操作之前，请确保你已经按照以上内容成功搭建博客，并且能使用<code>username.github.io</code>访问到自己的博客网站</p></div><h3 id="Github-Actions-简介"><a href="#Github-Actions-简介" class="headerlink" title="Github Actions 简介"></a>Github Actions 简介</h3><p>Actions是GitHub提供的自动化服务，可以在仓库中定义工作流，当发生特定事件（如 push 代码）时自动执行构建、部署等任务。这就是所谓的CI&#x2F;CD（持续集成与持续部署）<a href="https://docs.github.com/en/actions/get-started/understand-github-actions">参考说明</a></p><p>以此教程举例，当使用Github Actions后，我们只需要将配置好的源码推送到目标仓库，GitHub就会自动触发构建并部署。这样一来，就不必在本地反复执行“一键三连命令”<br>更重要的是，它大大增加了<strong>跨设备和无环境的便捷性</strong>：你即使没有本地开发环境，只用浏览器也能对文章进行编辑。</p><h3 id="申请令牌"><a href="#申请令牌" class="headerlink" title="申请令牌"></a>申请令牌</h3><div class="mermaid-wrap"><pre class="mermaid-src" data-config="{&quot;themeVariables&quot;: { &quot;fontSize&quot;: &quot;16px&quot; }, &quot;layout&quot;: &quot;elk&quot;, &quot;look&quot;: &quot;handDrawn&quot;}" hidden>    graph TD    %% 类定义：低饱和色+圆润边角，区分节点类型    classDef startNode fill:#e8f5e9, color:#2e7d32, stroke:#4caf50, stroke-width:2px, rx:8, ry:8, fontSize:13px    classDef processNode fill:#e3f2fd, color:#1565c0, stroke:#2196f3, stroke-width:2px, rx:8, ry:8, fontSize:13px    classDef endNode fill:#fff3e0, color:#e65100, stroke:#ff9800, stroke-width:2px, rx:8, ry:8, fontSize:13px    %% 主流程    A[👤 点击 GitHub 右上角头像] --&gt; B[⚙️ Settings&lt;br&gt;设置]    B --&gt; C[🔧 Developer settings&lt;br&gt;开发者设置]    C --&gt; D[🔑 Personal access tokens&lt;br&gt;个人访问令牌]    D --&gt; E[✨ Generate new token&lt;br&gt;生成新令牌]    %% 右侧提示（通过虚线连接D）    D -.-&gt; F[❗ 请选择 “Classic Token（经典）”&lt;br&gt;不要选 fine-grained]    %% 应用样式类    class A startNode    class B,C,D processNode    class F processNode    class E endNode    %% 连线样式：主流程实线、F为虚线    linkStyle 0 stroke:#4caf50, stroke-width:1.5px, stroke-opacity:0.8    linkStyle 1 stroke:#2196f3, stroke-width:1.5px, stroke-opacity:0.8    linkStyle 2 stroke:#2196f3, stroke-width:1.5px, stroke-opacity:0.8    linkStyle 3 stroke:#2196f3, stroke-width:1.5px, stroke-opacity:0.8    linkStyle 4 stroke:#2196f3, stroke-width:1.5px, stroke-opacity:0.8, stroke-dasharray: 5 5  </pre></div><p><strong>图片</strong><br>取一个备注，选择<code>No expiration</code> 不过期，勾选<code>repo,workflow</code> 将生成的令牌复制下来备用</p><h3 id="创建仓库"><a href="#创建仓库" class="headerlink" title="创建仓库"></a>创建仓库</h3><p>这个仓库用于存放博客源码；仓库名随意，可见性选择私人(Private)<br><strong>图片</strong></p><h3 id="配置-Secrets"><a href="#配置-Secrets" class="headerlink" title="配置 Secrets"></a>配置 Secrets</h3><p>在刚刚新建的仓库中点击<code>Settings</code><br><strong>图片</strong></p><p><code>Name</code>填写：<code>DEPLOYTOKEN</code><br>将刚刚复制的令牌值粘贴到<code>Secret</code>最后点击保存。<br><strong>图片</strong></p><h3 id="创建-workflow-文件"><a href="#创建-workflow-文件" class="headerlink" title="创建 workflow 文件"></a>创建 workflow 文件</h3><p>回到终端，在你的博客根目录分别执行这两行命令</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir -p .github/workflows</span><br><span class="line">touch .github/workflows/deploy.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Hexo</span> <span class="string">Blog</span> <span class="string">CI/CD</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">on:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">push:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">branches:</span> [<span class="string">main</span>, <span class="string">master</span>]</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">paths:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&#x27;**/*.json&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&#x27;**/*.yml&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&#x27;source/**&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&#x27;_config.yml&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&#x27;.github/workflows/**&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">jobs:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">build-deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">runs-on:</span> <span class="string">ubuntu-latest</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">env:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">TZ:</span> <span class="string">Asia/Shanghai</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">timeout-minutes:</span> <span class="number">15</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 【重要】如果部署失败，请在这里添加权限声明</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">permissions:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">contents:</span> <span class="string">write</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">steps:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">uses:</span> <span class="string">actions/checkout@v4</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">uses:</span> <span class="string">actions/setup-node@v4</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">with:</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">node-version:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;22&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">cache:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;npm&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Install</span> <span class="string">dependencies</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">run:</span> <span class="string">npm</span> <span class="string">ci</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Build</span> <span class="string">blog</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">run:</span> <span class="string">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">          npx hexo clean</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">          npx hexo generate</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span>        <span class="comment"># 静态文件会生成在默认的 /public 目录下</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment"># 【新部署步骤：使用 peaceiris/actions-gh-pages】</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Deploy</span> <span class="string">to</span> <span class="string">external</span> <span class="string">repo</span> <span class="string">main</span> <span class="string">branch</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">uses:</span> <span class="string">peaceiris/actions-gh-pages@v4</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">with:</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="comment"># 1. 密钥：使用我们在 Secret 中创建的高权限 Token</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="comment"># 注意：这里必须是你在步骤二中设置的 Secret 名称</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">personal_token:</span> <span class="string">$&#123;&#123;</span> <span class="string">secrets.DEPLOYTOKEN</span> <span class="string">&#125;&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="comment"># 2. 部署目录：Hexo 静态文件的默认输出目录</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">publish_dir:</span> <span class="string">./public</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="comment"># 3. 目标仓库：另一个仓库的完整地址</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="comment"># 格式：&lt;用户名&gt;/&lt;仓库名&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">external_repository:</span> <span class="string">ametoyuki098/nlozop</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="comment"># 4. 目标分支：你指定的 main 分支</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">publish_branch:</span> <span class="string">main</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="comment"># 5. 提交信息：</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">commit_message:</span> <span class="string">&quot;feat: Blog deployed via GH Actions [skip ci]&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Success</span> <span class="string">notification</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">run:</span> <span class="string">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;🎉 Blog deployed successfully!&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>复制上面的配置内容并放入deploy.yml</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nano .github/workflows/deploy.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在其中找到<code>external_repository</code>字段，根据注释修改成你自己的。最后保存退出</p><h3 id="推送触发"><a href="#推送触发" class="headerlink" title="推送触发"></a>推送触发</h3><p>根目录编辑<code>nano .gitignore</code>，内容如下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public/</span><br><span class="line">.deploy_git/</span><br><span class="line">db.json</span><br><span class="line">node_modules/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>还是在你的博客根目录依次执行Git命令</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init</span><br><span class="line">git add .</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;first commit&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git branch -M main</span><br><span class="line">git remote add origin git@github.com:ametoyuki098/Lopez.git</span><br><span class="line">git push -u origin main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这些命令与仓库地址可以在你刚刚创建的仓库主页中看到。<br><strong>图片</strong><br><code>git push...</code>执行后，去仓库点击<code>Actions</code>就能看见正在运行的工作流；等变成绿色说明成功完成。</p><p>访问<code>username.github.io</code></p><p>新建一篇文章，并重新推送；验证是否触发自动部署</p><ol><li>输入 <code>hexo new &quot;文章名称&quot;</code></li><li><code>git add .</code> 重新添加暂存</li><li><code>git commit -m &quot;填写备注信息&quot;</code></li><li>推送GitHub仓库：<code>git push</code></li></ol><p>稍等一会后重新访问<code>username.github.io</code> 查看是否有新建文章。</p><p><span style="color:red;">这是红色文字</span></p><div class="mermaid-wrap"><pre class="mermaid-src" data-config="{&quot;themeVariables&quot;: { &quot;fontSize&quot;: &quot;16px&quot; }, &quot;layout&quot;: &quot;elk&quot;, &quot;look&quot;: &quot;handDrawn&quot;}" hidden>    graph TD    %% 类定义：低饱和色+圆润边角，区分节点类型    classDef startNode fill:#e8f5e9, color:#2e7d32, stroke:#4caf50, stroke-width:2px, rx:8, ry:8, fontSize:13px    classDef processNode fill:#e3f2fd, color:#1565c0, stroke:#2196f3, stroke-width:2px, rx:8, ry:8, fontSize:13px    classDef endNode fill:#fff3e0, color:#e65100, stroke:#ff9800, stroke-width:2px, rx:8, ry:8, fontSize:13px    %% 主流程    A[👤 点击 GitHub 右上角头像] --&gt; B[⚙️ Settings&lt;br&gt;设置]    B --&gt; C[🔧 Developer settings&lt;br&gt;开发者设置]    C --&gt; D[🔑 Personal access tokens&lt;br&gt;个人访问令牌]    D --&gt; E[✨ Generate new token&lt;br&gt;生成新令牌]    %% 右侧提示（通过虚线连接D）    D -.-&gt; F[❗ 请选择 “Classic Token（经典）”&lt;br&gt;不要选 fine-grained]    %% 应用样式类    class A startNode    class B,C,D processNode    class F processNode    class E endNode    %% 连线样式：主流程实线、F为虚线    linkStyle 0 stroke:#4caf50, stroke-width:1.5px, stroke-opacity:0.8    linkStyle 1 stroke:#2196f3, stroke-width:1.5px, stroke-opacity:0.8    linkStyle 2 stroke:#2196f3, stroke-width:1.5px, stroke-opacity:0.8    linkStyle 3 stroke:#2196f3, stroke-width:1.5px, stroke-opacity:0.8    linkStyle 4 stroke:#2196f3, stroke-width:1.5px, stroke-opacity:0.8, stroke-dasharray: 5 5  </pre></div>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;介绍：此博文记录在安卓手机（平板）termux中安装配置hexo博客的过程，主题使用以及托管。&lt;/p&gt;
